name: pametnik u shumenu, kubrat 2 od 6 colourized
description: Part of a series of drawings of my favourite monument, the Monument to 1300 Years of Bulgarian History, location in Shumen Bulgaria.. The cubist monument sits on top of a hill located in Shumen, and depicts the kings of Bulgaria, pictured here is kubrat. This coloured piece is a collaboration with blissofart.tez (@blissofart on twitter), and I am so happy with the results
